President Obama has announced his intent to appoint Dori Henry as Assistant Secretary for Public Affairs at the Department of Labor and Robin L. Diamonte as a member of the Pension Benefit Guaranty Corporation. Dori Henry is currently the Senior Managing Director in the Office of Public Affairs at the Department of Labor and has been serving as Acting Assistant Secretary for Public Affairs since January 2016. Robin L. Diamonte is the Chief Investment Officer at United Technologies Corporation and has been a member of the Pension Benefit Guaranty Corporation since 2013.